data.title: A Key To Dutch History
data.meta_description: A Key to Dutch History - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. A Key to Dutch History report by the committee for the development of the dutch canon. Seventeen crew members were forced to spend the winter on the island of Nova Zembla in the northernmost part of Russia. A lot of the crew's belongings remained behind on the island including cutlery, clothing, weapons, books, tools and this clock.
